court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

attorneys: Motion of The National Association of Criminal Defense Lawyers for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Alabama denied.
casebody.head_matter:
Lam LUONG, petitioner,
v.
ALABAMA.
No. 15-922.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 28, 2016.
Motion of The National Association of Criminal Defense Lawyers for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Alabama denied.
